{
  "id": "adv_group_tri_01_04",
  "title": "TRINITYAiLE 01 04",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃ～ん、おはよう\n今日も一緒にレッスンがんばろな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ Rui-chan.\nLet's do our best at the lesson together again today~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 6.083809471130371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "…………ちょっと近い気がするんだけど？\n腕当たってるし、いつのまにか名前呼びだし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…………Don’t you think you're a bit too close?\nYour arm is touching me‚ and you’re calling me by my first name all of a sudden…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8,
      "endTime": 12.653287982940675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 9.366666666666669
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "別に友達やし、いいやん\nそんなことより……瑠依ちゃん、ええ香りするなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re friends‚ it’s fine.\nMore importantly… You smell nice‚ Rui-chan~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.846479730683614,
      "endTime": 19.03214848526125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 12.846479730683646
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "もう！　人前であからさまに匂い嗅がないでよ……\n……シャンプーか何かじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Geez! Don’t sniff me so obviously in public…\n…Isn’t it just my shampoo?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.21314639735028,
      "endTime": 25.01314639735028,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 19.21314639735031
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなん？　なんやええ香りやし\nうちも使うてみようかなぁ……後で商品名教えてな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? It smells nice‚ so\nI might try using it too… Tell me what it’s called later~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.213146397350283,
      "endTime": 32.8529648749809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 25.213146397350314
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 33.049398045617394
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "（……なんでこんなに懐かれてるのかしら）\n（何もトイレにまでついてこなくてもいいのに）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…I wonder why she’s being so friendly?)\n(She doesn’t have to follow me to the bathroom…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.049398045617394,
      "endTime": 39.00669947155123,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "練習生A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainee",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ねえ、また鈴村さん、天動さんと一緒にいる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Suzumura-san’s with Tendo-san again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.21274641158273,
      "endTime": 44.84607974491606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 39.212746411582756
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "練習生A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainee",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "なんかベタベタし過ぎじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aren't they being a little too clingy?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.846079744916054,
      "endTime": 47.67285974623849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "練習生B",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainee",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ほら、鈴村さんのお母さんって有名人だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ Suzumura-san’s mother is a celebrity‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.879413078249385,
      "endTime": 52.24607974491605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 47.879413078249385
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "練習生B",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainee",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "きっと鈴村さんのコネ狙いだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so she’s definitely after Suzumura-san’s connections.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.246079744916045,
      "endTime": 55.02941298288196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "…………っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…………Ugh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.246079744916045,
      "endTime": 56.68376683197506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 56.883766831975066
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "どないしたん、瑠依ちゃん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s wrong‚ Rui-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.883766831975066,
      "endTime": 59.05224751434812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "……やっぱり、もう少し離れてくれない？\n友達って言ってくれるのは嬉しいんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Would you mind giving me a little more space?\nI’m happy that you call me your friend‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.75043349864173,
      "endTime": 65.4561933100431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 59.75043349864176
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 65.9171001653084
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "私は、誰の力も頼りたくないの\n誰かと仲良くするつもりも……ないのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t want to rely on anyone’s help.\nI don’t intend to get close to anyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.9171001653084,
      "endTime": 73.40261032384721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "トップアイドルの地位を、自分の力だけで勝ち取る\nそう決めてるから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve decided that I will achieve the status of a top idol on my own.\n…That’s what I’ve decided.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.75043349864173,
      "endTime": 79.88376683197505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 80.28376683197506
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "……周りの声が、気に入らんの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Do you mind what people are saying?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.28376683197506,
      "endTime": 82.79644264183528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 83.28376683197506
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "……気付いていたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You knew?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.28376683197506,
      "endTime": 84.6951047321368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 85.15043349864172
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "うちもよく噂される方やし、結構耳がええからなぁ\nそうなんちゃうかなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I tend to be the subject of rumors‚ and I have pretty good hearing‚ ya know.\nI had a feeling that was it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.15043349864172,
      "endTime": 92.20043349864171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 92.55043349864172
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "そんなら分かった。うちは瑠依ちゃんから離れる……\n寂しいけどなぁ、ふふっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand. I’ll stay away from you then‚ Rui-chan…\nIt’s a shame though‚ chuckles",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.55043349864172,
      "endTime": 100.71710016530842,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6600.000000000008,
          "startTime": 99.15043349864173
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_01_04-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめんなさい、鈴村さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’m sorry‚ Suzumura-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.15043349864172,
      "endTime": 103.72070551516698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 101.15043349864173
    },
